text: α-Pyrrolidinoheptaphenone (PV8, α-PHPP) is a designer drug of the pyrrolidinophenone class of cathinones. It is the higher homolog of α-pyrrolidinohexiophenone (α-PHP). In the United States, α-pyrrolidinoheptaphenone is a Schedule I Controlled Substance. ==References== Category:Pyrrolidinophenones
title: Α-Pyrrolidinoheptaphenone
